rink\" your pores. They're nothing but small openings in the skin -- because they don't have muscles, they can't open or close. So although you can't physically change the structure of your pores by making them smaller, there are things that you can do to minimize their appearance<a href=\"http://health.howstuffworks.com/skin-care/problems/treating/shrink-large-pores.htm\">$^1$<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n","answer_id":31005,"question_id":30984,"up_vote_count":5}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/30984/do-sweat-pores-change-diameter","last_activity_date":1428002139,"creation_date":1427956084,"answer_count":1,"title":"Do sweat pores change diameter?","body":"<p>In <a href=\"http://www.cholinergicurticaria.net/cholinergic-urticaria-causes-what-causes-cholinergic-urticaria-to-develop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cholinergic Urticaria<\/a>, some people believe that the itching which is generally more in winters might be because that the diameter of sweat pores is less due to less activity(less sweat production) and in summers the diameter is usually more due to high activity (more sweat production). <\/p>\n\n<p><strong>Question:<\/strong> Hence the question in general, <strong>Do sweat pores change diameter?<\/strong><\/p>\n","question_id":30984,"tags":["skin","allergies","heat"],"score":4,"accepted_answer_id":31005,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":109,"up_vote_count":4,"last_edit_date":1428002139},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/aioWT.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":15066,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/15066/quality","reputation":197,"display_name":"Quality","accept_rate":80},"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/85bb9e2c9145ecb17430d6fdb574410f?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":12909,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/12909/dustin","reputation":2006,"display_name":"dustin"},"score":0,"post_id":30956,"edited":false